# app/src-tauri/binaries/ — the aibender-core sidecar staging dir.
#
# The built sidecar artifacts are LARGE (a Node runtime copy) and machine/
# target-specific — they are produced by scripts/build-sidecar.sh during
# `tauri build` and MUST NOT be committed. Only this .gitignore and README.md
# are tracked, so the directory exists in a fresh checkout (Tauri's
# externalBin resolves the path at bundle time; the debug/--smoke-test build
# never touches it).
*
!.gitignore
!README.md
